      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... why would i want to tend to fragments? there's no warmth in ash. it's just cold and gray. it feels kind of pointless to keep dragging this shell around, eating and sleeping and walking around, when the person who was supposed to be living this life is already gone. it feels like a chore. like i'm just performing a role for no one.",
